{"tid":1591304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"10月1行動 文宣入","createTime":"2019-09-24T05:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T06:40:22.000Z","uid":207071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3bca18c7362c2958781bcf6abd576d9df744ba59","tid":1591304,"uid":207071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:53:14.000Z","msg":"其實點解一定要港島<br />\n話集中個啲係咪岸鳩 啲狗就係要集中咁捉曬你地<br />\n上次8月5打後既記招已經講到明 一日已經嚴重過之前咁多次 <br />\n啫係點呀 啫係佢驚7區集會 我地分散戰線 令佢警力唔足夠應付我地咁多個地區 多過港島行街<br />\n港島行街 啲狗兩面包差 走都冇得走 <br />\n睇死你班撚樣都唔會攻過去 <br />\n啲狗嚟到又係搏拉 <br />\n咁點解唔分散戰鬥力 學7區咁 <br />\n今次應該針對返黨鐵 我唔撚信佢有咁多人守住啲入閘機<br />\n黨鐵已經提左我地 佢唔夠零件 點解唔食住個勢？<br />\n就算唔同意 都唔好淨係針對一個地方 因為黨鐵已經唔係服務我地。<br />\n唔該唔好戀戰港島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08146151ff23c8621a087be98caaa98d696b16c2","tid":1591304,"uid":207071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:53:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6abdcef6da0964cfb38846cfc523f4086cfa505c","tid":1591304,"uid":207071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1d04c12c03351d3575ee12507d6a1774fdaf5a0","tid":1591304,"uid":207071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:53:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97a068e9f773bd09afe6b095cd903d814c0948e7","tid":1591304,"uid":207071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48b7a8f14d0e9feabae72e62df79b2e9cf3c2f80","tid":1591304,"uid":207071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1285dba4477e973a1a026f18dad980a2ae8ecccd","tid":1591304,"uid":145254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:54:44.000Z","msg":"但前線唔夠人7區喎"},{"pid":"d0aa6ffdd5f2f13ff31616030544aad589b1c463","tid":1591304,"uid":207071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"呢個唔係各有各做既問題阿 <br />\n係好驚送頭 一直都講打游擊 <br />\